# Data Organization

## Folder Structure

All data is organized by country:

```
public/data/[country]/
├── speedmart/      # Retail location data
├── districts/      # District/region data
├── hotels/         # Hotel/accommodation data
├── geojson/        # Geographic boundaries
└── statistics/     # Statistical data (JSON/CSV)
```

